data.description: Incredible Opportunity in Baker School District! This wonderful home is a true gem, boasting a brand-new 30-year architectural roof installed in 2023—ensuring both durability and curb appeal for years to come. Step inside, and you'll be greeted by a fresh and inviting space, as the home has just been completely repainted. Warm colors and stained/scored concrete flooring throughout make cleaning up a breeze, offering both style and practicality. The open floor plan is perfect for entertaining, with the wood-burning fireplace serving as a focal point in the spacious living room. The kitchen is a chef's delight, boasting stained cabinets, ample countertop space, stainless steel appliances, and a full-length pop-up breakfast bar—ideal for casual dining and socializing. Both the living room and master bedroom showcases trey ceilings. The split bedroom plan ensures privacy, with the master bedroom featuring a walk-in closet and a relaxing garden tub in the bath. As you step outside to the covered back patio and unwind while overlooking your privacy fenced backyard ideal for outdoor gatherings. Additional features include a brand new HVAC unit installed in 2023, double garage, and low maintenance exterior vinyl siding. Don't let this opportunity slip away! All improvements per seller. Contact your favorite REALTOR today to schedule your personal showing and make this fantastic home yours before it's gone!
